# Codex Target

`.codex/*` is the Codex-side target layer generated by Agent Flow.

## Layout

- `agents/` -> rendered role contracts
- `skills/` -> rendered lifecycle skills plus installed pack skills
- `guides/` -> rendered methods and checklists
- `orchestration-policy.md` -> Codex-native entrypoint to the canonical lifecycle contract
- `claude-interop.md` -> parity contract between Claude and Codex target files

## Rules

- `AGENTS.md` is the root Codex entrypoint.
- Shared persisted artifacts live outside `.codex/` in the configured artifact paths:

{{artifacts.table}}

- Generated files should come from `agent-flow sync`, `agent-flow init`, or `agent-flow update`.
- Edit `.agent-flow/config.json` and installed packs instead of hand-editing generated mirrors.
- Manual project policy can live in normal project docs and be referenced through config.
